## Description
UD_Kyrgyz-KTMU is dependency parsing based treebank in Kyrgyz language. Sentences were selected
partly from Kyrgyz story and novel books, partly from Kyrgyz news websites.


The treebank consists of 781 sentences (7.4K tokens) for now and its domain is mainly news headlines.
Kyrgyz UD treebank follows the Universal Dependencies (UD) annotation standard.

## Acknowledgments
We would like to thank all the people who contributed to this corpus: Assoc.Prof.Dr. Bakit Sharshembaev

<h3>Verbs with Reflexive Core Objects</h3>

<ul>
  <li>This corpus contains 1 lemmas that occur at least once with a reflexive core object (<a>obj</a> or <a>iobj</a>). Examples: моюн өзүнүн</li>
</ul>

<h3>Relations Overview</h3>

<ul>
<li>This corpus uses 3 relation subtypes: <a>advmod:emph</a>, <a>compound:svc</a>, <a>nmod:poss</a></li>
<li>The following 14 relation types are not used in this corpus at all: <a>iobj</a>, <a>xcomp</a>, <a>vocative</a>, <a>expl</a>, <a>dislocated</a>, <a>aux</a>, <a>cop</a>, <a>appos</a>, <a>clf</a>, <a>list</a>, <a>orphan</a>, <a>goeswith</a>, <a>reparandum</a>, <a>dep</a></li>
</ul>
